How The Last Jedi Defies Expectations About Male Heroes

WOW! This is so thoughtful and cool!

 I never noticed these relations and actions of characters, and how the hateful male moviegoers might subconsciously see them!

You won’t give in, no matter how much this new heat in your veins burns.

blog.description: I am a descriptivist linguist for the Mando'a language. I show what it can do, not what it MUST do. All words and descriptions are taken from the mandoa.org Mandalorian Dictionary. Want to support this blog? Buy me a Kofi? OR buy some Mando'a themed items? Visit our Discord? Blog icon by Rina
